Package: libgrilo-0.1
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: grilo-0.1-plugins
Description: Grilo framework
 Grilo is a framework that provides access to different sources of
 multimedia content, using a pluggable system.
 .
 This package contains the core library and elements.

Package: libgrilo-0.1-dbg
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libgrilo-0.1
Description: Grilo framework debugging symbols
 Grilo is a framework that provides access to different sources of
 multimedia content, using a pluggable system.
 .
 This package contains unstripped shared libraries, useful to debug.

